# README

### What is this repository for?

-   Automation Test Suite for Right Hand Assignment 

---
---

### Prerequisites

```
This project is build on NodeJS platform
So the expectations are npm should be installed

https://nodejs.org/en/download/

PLease pick the compatible package based on the Operationg System

```


### How do I get set up?

Install dependencies

```sh
npm install
```

To run the tests in your local machine

```sh
npm run test
```

### Technologies

-   WebdriverIO used as Automation Tool
-   CucumberJS used for Automation Framework
-   Axios used to cover API Automation


### Framework Structure

-   features folder with have test scenarios written in gherkin language (Given, When Then) format
-   step-definitions will be having the actual automation scripts mapped with tests steps in features folder
-   pageobjects will be having the web element and associated methods 
-   reports will be having JSON and HTML test results
-   conig folder will contains the configuration for entite test automatino suite


### How to see HTML Report

-   Open reports folder through <project_folder>/reports/html
-   Open the index.html file in browser


